ntroller lost 2 life and then gained 8 life this turn, the player whose turn it is may draw a card.£11/8/2016: If your Commander deck has two commanders, you can only include cards whose own color identities are also found in your commanders’ combined color identities. If Akiri and Silas Renn are your commanders, your deck may contain cards with white, blue, black, and red in their color identity, but not green.£11/8/2016: Both commanders start in the command zone, and the remaining 98 cards of your deck are shuffled to become your library.£11/8/2016: To have two commanders, both must have the partner ability as the game begins. Losing the ability during the game doesn’t cause either to cease to be your commander.£11/8/2016: Once the game begins, your two commanders are tracked separately. If you cast one, you won’t have to pay an additional {2} the first time you cast the other. A player loses the game after having been dealt 21 damage from one of them, not from both of them combined. Command Beacon’s effect puts one into your hand from the command zone, not both.£11/8/2016: An effect that checks whether you control your commander is satisfied if you control one or both of your two commanders.','UR (O)',NULL,'N/A','1.24','N/A',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'UR','死灵炼金术士卢德维',NULL,'Ludevic, nécro-alchimiste','Ludevic, Nekro-Alchemist','Ludevic, Necro-Alchimista','屍錬金術師、ルーデヴィック','Ludevic, Necroalquimista',NULL,'Ludevic, necroalquimista',NULL,'传奇生物～人类／法术师',NULL,'Créature légendaire : humain et sorcier','Legendäre Kreatur — Mensch, Zauberer','Creatura Leggendaria — Mago Umano','伝説のクリーチャー ― 人間・ウィザード','Criatura Lendária — Humano Mago',NULL,'Criatura legendaria — Hechicero humano',NULL,'在每位牌手的结束步骤开始时，对该牌手而言，如果本回合中曾有你以外的牌手失去生命，则他可以抓一张牌。£拍档（你可将两个具有拍档异能的生物共同用作指挥官。）',NULL,'Au début de l''étape de fin de chaque joueur, ce joueur peut piocher une carte si un joueur autre que vous a perdu des points de vie ce tour-ci.£Partenariat #_(Vous pouvez avoir deux commandants si les deux ont le partenariat.)_#','Zu Beginn des Endsegments jedes Spielers kann jener Spieler eine Karte ziehen, falls ein Spieler außer dir in diesem Zug Lebenspunkte verloren hat.£Partner #_(Du kannst zwei Kommandeure haben, falls beide Partner haben.)_#','All''inizio della sottofase finale di ogni giocatore, quel giocatore può pescare una carta se un giocatore diverso da te ha perso punti vita in questo turno.£Partner #_(Puoi avere due comandanti se entrambi hanno partner.)_#','各プレイヤーの終了ステップの開始時に、そのプレイヤーは、あなた以外のプレイヤーがこのターンにライフを失っていたなら、カードを１枚引いてもよい。£共闘（両方が共闘を持つなら、あなたは２体の統率者を使用できる。）','No início da etapa final de cada jogador, aquele jogador pode comprar um card se um jogador que não seja você perdeu pontos de vida neste turno.£Parceiro #_(Você pode ter dois comandantes se ambos tiverem parceiro.)_#',NULL,'Al comienzo del paso final de cada jugador, ese jugador puede robar una carta si otro jugador que no seas tú perdió una o más vidas este turno.£Camarada. #_(Puedes tener dos comandantes si ambos tienen camarada.)_#',NULL,'#_「怎样才能自学成才？显然，需要有脑子。」_#',NULL,'#_« Comment devient-on un génie autodidacte ? Naturellement, il faut avoir de la cervelle. »_#','#_„Wie man autodidaktisch zum Genie wird? Nun, man benötigt dafür ein Gehirn."_#','#_"Come si diventa un genio autodidatta? Naturalmente, ci vuole cervello."_#','#_「どうすれば独学で天才になれるのか、だと？とりあえず脳が必要だ。」_#','#_"Como alguém se torna um gênio autodidata? Usando o cérebro, naturalmente."_#',NULL,'#_"¿Cómo se convierte uno en un genio autodidacta? Pues con cerebro, está claro"._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('420773','Lurking Predators','C16','Enchantment','R','{4}{G}{G}','6',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Whenever an opponent casts a spell, reveal the top card of your library. If it''s a creature card, put it onto the battlefield. Otherwise, you may put that card on the bottom of your library.','#_All are prey to the eyes of the wild._#',NULL,'Mike Bierek','156','5','£10/1/2009: If an opponent casts a spell, this ability triggers and is put on the stack on top of that spell. This ability will resolve (meaning that a revealed creature card will enter the battlefield) before the spell resolves.£10/1/2009: You must put the revealed card onto the battlefield if it’s a creature card. If it’s not a creature card and you don’t put it on the bottom of your library, it stops being revealed and simply remains on top of your library.£10/1/2009: A “creature card” is any card with the type creature, even if it has other types such as artifact, enchantment, or land. Older cards of type summon are also creature cards.','G',NULL,'2.62','4.04','10.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','潜伏掠食者',NULL,'Prédateurs en maraude','Lauernde Raubtiere','Predatori in Agguato','隠れ潜む捕食者','Predadores à Espreita',NULL,'Depredadores furtivos',NULL,'结界',NULL,'Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento',NULL,'Encantamiento',NULL,'每当任一对手施放咒语时，展示你的牌库顶牌。若该牌是生物牌，则将之放进战场。若否，则你可以将该牌置于你牌库底。',NULL,'À chaque fois qu''un adversaire lance un sort, révélez la carte du dessus de votre bibliothèque. Si c''est une carte de créature, mettez-la sur le champ de bataille. Sinon, vous pouvez mettre cette carte au-dessous de votre bibliothèque.','Immer wenn ein Gegner einen Zauberspruch wirkt, decke die oberste Karte deiner Bibliothek auf. Falls es eine Kreaturenkarte ist, bringe sie ins Spiel. Anderenfalls kannst du sie unter deine Bibliothek legen.','Ogniqualvolta un avversario lancia una magia, rivela la prima carta del tuo grimorio. Se è una carta creatura, mettila sul campo di battaglia. Altrimenti, puoi metterla in fondo al tuo grimorio.','対戦相手が呪文を１つ唱えるたび、あなたは自分のライブラリーの一番上のカードを公開する。それがクリーチャー・カードであるなら、それを戦場に出す。そうでないなら、あなたはそのカードをあなたのライブラリーの一番下に置いてもよい。','Toda vez que um oponente conjurar uma mágica, revele o card do topo de seu grimório. Se for um card de criatura, coloque-o no campo de batalha. Do contrário, você pode colocar aquele card no fundo de seu grimório.',NULL,'Siempre que un oponente lance un hechizo, muestra la p