,NULL),('420620','Orzhov Advokist','C16','Creature — Human Advisor','U','{2}{W}','3','1','4',NULL,'At the beginning of your upkeep, each player may put two +1/+1 counters on a creature they control. If a player does, creatures that player controls can''t attack you or a planeswalker you control until your next turn.','#_The Orzhov care not for repentance, only repayment._#',NULL,'Jason A. Engle','3','5','£11/8/2016: While resolving Orzhov Advokist’s ability, you choose a creature you control or choose not to put any counters on a creature, then each other player in turn order does the same. Each player will know the choices made by players who chose before them. Then simultaneously each player who chose a creature puts two +1/+1 counters on the creature they chose.£11/8/2016: Orzhov Advokist’s ability doesn’t target the creatures that receive +1/+1 counters. Their controllers choose them as the ability resolves. Players can’t take actions between making their choices and the +1/+1 counters being placed.£11/8/2016: If a player chooses to accept Orzhov Advokist’s gift, that player can’t attack you or a planeswalker you control with any creatures during their next turn, even creatures that weren’t on the battlefield as Orzhov Advokist’s ability resolved.£11/8/2016: Orzhov Advokist’s effect keeps creatures from attacking you even if Orzhov Advokist leaves the battlefield, if the creature that received counters is no longer on the battlefield, or if an effect has moved those counters off of the creature that received them and put them onto another creature.','W',NULL,'0.28','0.45','3.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','欧佐夫倡议人',NULL,'Avoquiste d''Orzhov','Orzhov-Advokistin','Fautrice Orzhov','オルゾフの弁護士','Advoquista Orzhov',NULL,'Abogada orzhov',NULL,'生物～人类／参谋',NULL,'Créature : humain et conseiller','Kreatur — Mensch, Berater','Creatura — Consigliere Umano','クリーチャー ― 人間・アドバイザー','Criatura — Humano Conselheiro',NULL,'Criatura — Consejero humano',NULL,'在你的维持开始时，每位牌手各可以在一个由其操控的生物上放置两个+1/+1指示物。若有牌手如此作，则直到你的下一个回合，由该牌手操控的生物不能攻击你或由你操控的鹏洛客。',NULL,'Au début de votre entretien, chaque joueur peut mettre deux marqueurs +1/+1 sur une créature qu''il contrôle. Si un joueur fait ainsi, les créatures que ce joueur contrôle ne peuvent pas vous attaquer ou attaquer un planeswalker que vous contrôlez jusqu''à votre prochain tour.','Zu Beginn deines Versorgungssegments kann jeder Spieler zwei +1/+1-Marken auf eine Kreatur legen, die er kontrolliert. Falls ein Spieler dies tut, können Kreaturen, die dieser Spieler kontrolliert, bis zu deinem nächsten Zug weder dich noch einen Planeswalker, den du kontrollierst, angreifen.','All''inizio del tuo mantenimento, ogni giocatore può mettere due segnalini +1/+1 su una creatura che controlla. Se un giocatore lo fa, le creature controllate da quel giocatore non possono attaccare te o un planeswalker che controlli fino al tuo prossimo turno.','あなたのアップキープの開始時に、各プレイヤーは自分がコントロールするクリーチャー１体の上に＋１/＋１カウンターを２個置いてもよい。いずれかのプレイヤーがそうしたなら、あなたの次のターンまで、そのプレイヤーがコントロールするクリーチャーではあなたやあなたがコントロールするプレインズウォーカーを攻撃できない。','No início de sua manutenção, cada jogador pode colocar dois marcadores +1/+1 em uma criatura que ele controla. Se um jogador fizer isso, as criaturas que aquele jogador controle não poderão atacar você nem um planeswalker que você controle até seu próximo turno.',NULL,'Al comienzo de tu mantenimiento, cada jugador puede poner dos contadores +1/+1 sobre una criatura que controla. Si un jugador lo hace, las criaturas que controla ese jugador no pueden atacarte a ti o a un planeswalker que controlas hasta tu próximo turno.',NULL,'#_欧佐夫并不在乎你是否悔过，只在乎你是否赔过。_#',NULL,'#_Les Orzhov se moquent du repentir, ils s''intéressent seulement au remboursement._#','#_Die Orzhov sind nicht an Reue, sondern ausschließlich an Tilgung interessiert._#','#_Agli Orzhov non interessa il pentimento, solo il pagamento._#','#_オルゾフは謝罪を求めず、返済を求める。_#','#_Aos Orzhov não importa que alguém se arrependa, só que alguém pague._#',NULL,'#_Los Orzhov no buscan el arrep